bHideEditorDataLayers: True when the Data Layer Outliner is displaying Editor Data Layers
bHideRuntimeDataLayers: True when the Data Layer Outliner is displaying Runtime Data Layers
bHideDataLayerActors: True when the Data Layer Outliner is not displaying actors
bHideUnloadedActors: True when the Data Layer Outliner is not displaying unloaded actors
bShowOnlySelectedActors: True when the Data Layer Outliner is only displaying actors and datalayers for selected actors
bHighlightSelectedDataLayers: True when the Data Layer Outliner highlights Data Layers containing actors that are currently selected
bHideLevelInstanceContent: True when the Data Layer Outliner is not displaying Level Instance content
